Root cause: pipeline confused two different data sources:
- Column A: Vendor content ppm (what the batch actually contains)
- Column B: USP <467> regulatory limit ppm (what's allowed)
- AI used Column B for ingredient rows AND comparison row.

Column A goes in ingredient rows (component × solvent cells).
Column B goes in the final comparison row (Limit as per USP <467>).

